<li id="cite_note-3"><b><a href="#cite_ref-3" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://dir.salon.com/story/ent/masterpiece/2002/04/08/outer_limits/index.html?CP=IMD&amp;DN=110" class="external autonumber" title="http://dir.salon.com/story/ent/masterpiece/2002/04/08/outer_limits/index.html?CP=IMD&amp;DN=110" rel="nofollow">[3]</a></li>
